OverviewSpecializationsSolutionsOverview
Magic Software Enterprises (NASDAQ: MGIC) is a global provider of application platforms and business integration solutions. Our business technology gives partners and customers the power to efficiently build, deploy, and integrate IT applications.Magic Software has offices in 15 countries covering in total more than 50 countries with a global network of ISVs, system integrators, value-added distributors and resellers, consulting and OEM partners. The company’s award-winning code-free solutions give partners and customers the power to leverage existing IT resources, enhance business agility and focus on core business priorities. Magic Software’s technological approach, product roadmap and corporate strategy are recognized by leading industry analysts. 
