Magic Software UpgradeAutomatic Upgrade of Magic Software Applications to Magic Xpa, and Conversion of Underlying Databases to SQL  





                        Key Advantages of this Solution                    











                                        Simple                                    

                                        RISK FREE MAGIC XPA OR SQL UPGRADE WITH ZERO OBLIGATION                                    




Upgrade your Magic Software application or uniPaaS application to the latest version of Magic xpa, including full training for your developer team
Convert your Magic Software application's underlying database from Btrieve / Pervasive to SQL Database
Full backwards compatibility with previous magic software versions guaranteed
All Magic Software and uniPaaS or Magic Xpa versions supported, as well as all database types used by Magic Software applications
Risk Free Magic Software Upgrade with NO code freeze
Try before you buy
 










                                        Quick                                    

                                        FASTEST MAGIC SOFTWARE CONVERSION ON THE MARKET                                    




The upgraded magic xpa application retains its original application methodology, so assimilation is quick and easy
Completely automated Magic Xpa upgrade tool and SQL DB Conversion tool, mitigates the need for any additional manual work
Automated solution enables your upgraded Magic Software Xpa application to be operational very quickly
Delivery of migrated code in 5 days or less
Go live within 4 weeks
 










                                        Effective                                    

                                        CHEAPER THAN ALL OTHER ALTERNATIVES                                    




Improves code quality during Magic Xpa upgrade or SQL upgrade,  while embedding new features and abilities of the magic xpa version
Incorporate face-lifting or performance improvement package during the Magic xpa upgrade
Full solution for all .NET issues and 3rd-party components
Support all Magic old versions and uniPaaS or Magic Xpa version
 










                        Why Choose Go Up Technology?                    

Go Up Technology provides a completely automatic upgrade process that is quicker, more effective, and more economical than any alternative solutions.
Automatic upgrading permits the application methodology to be retained, while enabling optimization of the application’s architecture and GUI. 














                        Technical Description
                    






Compatibility with Previous Versions

                            Maintain your Magic Software application's functionality and compatibility with previous versions, while improving its code by replacing old methods with new ones.                        
xpa Improves Capabilities

                            Magic xpa provides new embedded capabilities that developers can leverage in a simple and easy way. Some of these capabilities necessitate certain new definitions in the application.                         
Record Main Conversion

                            Full conversion of Record Main to Handlers, removing dead code, and fixing logical bugs in your Magic Xpa code.
                        
Issues Arising from .NET Deployment

                            Handling all issues related to .NET deplopyment include replacing old DLLs such as Get.dll or Hotfudge.dll, and replacing ActiveX with Native .NET resources.                        
Combine Database Covnersion to SQL

                            Database conversions can be integrated with any other conversion.
Improve performances and security of the database.
support Pervasive to SQL, Btrieve to SQL or Any database supported by Magic Software.                        












